                            <comment id="14135971" author="jmhsieh" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 18:59:45 +0000"  >
&lt;p&gt;Pending mob work is targeted for 100k-10mb range.  tbd to see if it is makes sens for 10mb-64mb.  (if you have a few it would be ok, but if you have a lot).&lt;/p&gt;

